class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/massimiliano-maurizi/">View all articles by Massimiliano Maurizi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/06/cajkovskij-uno-e-due-al-malibran/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Čajkovskij uno e due al Malibran</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/06/pechino-celebra-lopera-lirica/" rel="next">Pechino celebra l&#8217;Opera Lirica <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-17779"> <article id="comment-17779" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cd6b86400849d64bac209022cc4d035d?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Mariano</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/06/un-ballo-in-maschera-a-santa-cecilia/#comment-17779"><time datetime="2013-06-23T14:52:29+00:00">23 giugno 2013 at 14:52</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Concordo al 110% col giudizio su Meli; un po&#8217; meno sugli altri protagonisti. Comunque qualcosa al di soèpra della media.</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respon